<i>noun</i>: 화톳불 [화토뿔/화톧뿔], 모닥불 [모닥뿔] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>화톳불 [화토뿔/화톧뿔]</dt><br>
<dd>bonfire; wood fire</dd><br>
<dd>장작 등을 모아서 피워 놓은 불.</dd><br>
<dd>A fire made by burning firewood, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>모닥불 [모닥뿔]</dt><br>
<dd>bonfire</dd><br>
<dd>낙엽이나 나뭇가지 등을 모아 피우는 불.</dd><br>
<dd>A fire made with gathered leaves or twigs, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>